resources.string: Joe is a an eclectic visionary with a wide variety of experience with sound design. He can tackle any project head on, adding his own creative energy to keep every track expressive and innovative. Formerly of the band Between Myth & Legend, Joe made his way into the world of audio production 4 years ago, with a plethora of music business expertise to follow. His wide range of creativity will play a crucial role in your experience.
